            making a box(s) are:
                 
                 -w (window/region) [data=d][map plot=p]                                          _           _ 
                 -L (pen) [plotter pen location=value]                                                _____ 
            
            EXAMPLE            EXAMPLE
            The file misc/box draws a box in pen 6, 3 cm. away from the                     ________                                          
            bottom, right, top and left sides of the plotting window.
            
                 legend -m map.def -o ovm/box << EOF
                 -w p
                 -L 6
                  3.000  3.000       # origin point
                 >-3.000  3.000      # end bottom side
                 >-3.000 >-3.000     # end right side
                  3.000 >-3.000      # end top side
                  3.000  3.000       # end left side/end
                 .
                 EOF
            
            NOTE            NOTE
            If only one map element will be drawn on the map
            composition, the default selection for the file name is
            recommended for use.  The make.box file may be modified                                      ________                     
            through the text definition file to draw irregular shapes
            with straight sides.
            
            The delete key will abort the make.box command.                                          ________         
            
